- Home runs are a type of statistic in baseball where a player hits the ball and scores a run by circling all the bases; 
- Average home runs refer to the average number of home runs a player hits over a certain period; 
- Total contract value refers to the total amount of money a player is paid over the length of their contract.

sql:
SELECT AVG(payment_amount) AS average_salary
FROM contract_payments
WHERE payment_type = 'Salary';
